  "original_title": "\u0d86\u0db6\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dc4\u0dbb\u0daf\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0dc4\u0dd9\u0dc5\u0dcf \u0daf\u0d9a\u0dd3",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Attacking the disabled is condemned",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "In a statement, the organization 'Rights for Rights' says that it strongly condemns the false propaganda that people with disabilities were brutally attacked when the Galumuwadora activists were attacked on the 22nd and it is a baseless statement.",
        "The statement issued by the president of the organization, Nisha Sharif, further states that she condemns the efforts of some people to achieve narrow political goals under the guise of advocating for the rights of persons with disabilities."
      ],
